OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain across
OL,6,Fthe northwest will move southeastwards
OL,7,Facross the UK through this evening and
OL,8,Fovernight, but weakening as it moves
OL,9,Facross England and Wales. Drier behind
OL,10,Fthis, with some clear spells. Widely
OL,11,Fmild and staying warm in the southeast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FA largely sunny day,
OL,14,Falthough northwest Scotland, Northern
OL,15,FIreland and some western coasts
OL,16,Felsewhere often cloudier with some
OL,17,Fpatchy drizzle. Another very warm day
OL,18,Ffor most.
